Name: romanize3
Version: 0.1.14
Summary: Romanize - Transliteration module to romanize greek, hebrew, arabic, coptic, syriaic, phoenician, finnish, and sanskrit letters to the single roman letter equivalents and back
Home-page: https://github.com/markomanninen/romanize3
